description: Don,t miss your chance to own this BPDA affordable unit,  Located in Fort Point Place, an exclusive loft building in Boston's highly sought after Fort Point neighborhood. Ideally located just steps to Boston's Seaport, this meticulously studio loft features an open floor plan, high ceilings, oversized windows, exposed beams, and wide plank maple hardwood floors. The recently renovated kitchen features with custom cabinetry, quartz countertops, and new appliances and it also has a brand new bathroom. First group showing is Thursday, October 3rd, 6-730 and First Open House is Saturday October 5th 11:30am to 1:00pm
